{"tid":1816462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去到今日呢個境地 我真係好想同班分化撚/打手講","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T02:47:21.000Z","uid":41873,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e3b498bbe39442aa9ad1b370670b38fb9a7fbf","tid":1816462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"乜你地覺得係連登出幾篇文放下負<br />\n分化下我地就真係好成功？場運動就會完？<br />\n你地做緊咩我地心知肚明 知你地用左好多努力去令自已進步 了解下我地既弱點 再慢慢從我地既弱點進攻<br />\n但我想講 連登一向都係平行時空黎 我好相信就算無連登<br />\n只要五大訴求一日未達成<br />\n場運動一日都唔會完<br />\n希望各位打手/分化撚/黑警hack既ac睇到會醒少少 唔好再咁弱智on9覺得出幾篇文係咁洗個熱門就會有用<br />\n<br />\n再提提大家今日係周同學離開我地既兩個月<br />\n無論大家係今晚8點9分做緊咩都好<br />\n我好希望大家可以為周同學默哀一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n同埋星期日見"},{"pid":"66b3af0e040368cbb27b921f01b8001d53be19ff","tid":1816462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d334961093dbd74df2522472ad3a93648edace5","tid":1816462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fabf0495b78a44371eeba820522597829e96fc7","tid":1816462,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/LamCheng/permalink/936548510074322/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FLamCheng%2Fpermalink%2F936548510074322%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=5b9372fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/LamCheng/permalink/936548510074322/</a><br />\n（超突發！）有警察投稿：原來鄧狗搵左專業公關 ,連登出PO搞分化"},{"pid":"3f3b20e724fcc83f561eaecc18b621c2ff02b1b9","tid":1816462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0600e247acd7b8c479ed5b51ea68803cd22a99e","tid":1816462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d04edb74e472280939dff60